Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5), cmake, quilt, kdebase-workspace-dev (>=4:3.98.0~),
 kdebase-dev (>=4:3.98.0~), xscreensaver, xscreensaver-gl
Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: kdeartwork
Architecture: all
Depends: kdeartwork-misc (>= ${binary:Version}), kdeartwork-emoticons (>= ${binary:Version}),  kdeartwork-style (>= ${binary:Version}), kdeartwork-theme-icon (>= ${binary:Version}), kdeartwork-theme-window (>= ${binary:Version}), kdewallpapers (>= ${binary:Version}), kscreensaver (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: themes, styles and more from the official KDE release
 KDE (the K Desktop Environment) is a powerful Open Source graphical
 desktop environment for Unix workstations. It combines ease of use,
 contemporary functionality, and outstanding graphical design with the
 technological superiority of the Unix operating system.
 .
 This metapackage includes a collection of artistic extras (themes, widget
 styles, screen savers, wallpaper, icons, emoticons and so on) provided
 with the official release of KDE4.


Package: kdeartwork-misc
Architecture: all
Section: kde
Suggests: kworldclock
Description: various multimedia goodies released with KDE4
 This package contains miscellaneous multimedia goodies for KDE4.
 Included are additional KDE sounds and kworldclock themes.
 .
 This package is part of KDE4, and a component of the KDE artwork module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdeartwork' packages for more information.


Package: kdeartwork-emoticons
Architecture: all
Section: kde
Enhances: kopete
Description: emoticon collections for KDE4 chat clients
 This package contains several collections of emoticons used by official
 and unofficial KDE chat clients, such as Kopete and Konversation.
 .
 This package is part of KDE4, and a component of the KDE artwork module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdeartwork' packages for more information.


